SIMPLE: underfoot
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underfoot
<hw>Un`der*foot"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Under the feet;
underneath; below. See <cref>Under foot</cref>, under <er>Foot</er>,
<pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underfoot</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Underfoot
<hw>Un`der*foot"</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Low; base; abject; trodden
down.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underfringe</ent>⟦br⟧
